'''Johne's disease'''
# a [[chronic]], [[contagious]] and often [[fatal]] [[disease]] of [[cattle]], [[sheep]] and [[goat]]s, caused by the [[intestinal]] [[bacterium]] ''[[Mycobacterium paratuberculosis]]'', characterized by [[inflammation]] of the [[mucous membrane]]s of the [[gastrointestinal tract]]

